<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Thank You for Contacting Us - Quiz-Blog</title>
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #157A6E, #1e8e85);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }

        .header::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background: url('data:image/svg+xml,<svg width="60" height="60" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><defs><pattern id="a" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse" width="60" height="60"><circle cx="30" cy="30" r="2" fill="rgba(255,255,255,0.1)"/></pattern></defs><rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(%23a)"/></svg>');
            opacity: 0.3;
        }

        .header-icon {
            font-size: 60px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
            animation: bounce 1.5s ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes bounce {
            0%, 20%, 60%, 100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
            40% {
                transform: translateY(-10px);
            }
            80% {
                transform: translateY(-5px);
            }
        }

        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }

        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #157A6E;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .thank-you-card {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d4edda, #c3e6cb);
            border: 1px solid #c3e6cb;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .thank-you-card::before {
            content: '💌';
            position: absolute;
            top: 15px;
            right: 15px;
            font-size: 40px;
            opacity: 0.3;
        }

        .thank-you-message {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #155724;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .thank-you-description {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #155724;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .response-timeline {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #157A6E;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .timeline-title {
            color: #157A6E;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .timeline-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding: 15px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }

        .timeline-item:hover {
            transform: translateX(5px);
        }

        .timeline-icon {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-right: 15px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            color: #157A6E;
        }

        .timeline-text {
            color: #555;
            font-weight: 500;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .info-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e3f2fd, #bbdefb);
            border: 1px solid #bbdefb;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        .info-title {
            color: #0277bd;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .info-text {
            color: #01579b;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .cta-section {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #157A6E, #1e8e85);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-radius: 12px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .cta-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .cta-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .cta-button {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
        }

        .cta-button:hover {
            background: white;
            color: #157A6E;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }

        .company-info {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        .company-name {
            color: #157A6E;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .company-tagline {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .company-location {
            color: #333;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .social-links {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .social-link {
            color: #1f3fcf;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0 8px;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .social-link:hover {
            color: #157A6E;
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .separator {
            margin: 0 4px;
            color: #999;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 10px;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            
            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .footer {
                padding: 25px 20px;
            }

            .header-icon {
                font-size: 50px;
            }

            .cta-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .timeline-item {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .timeline-icon {
                margin-right: 0;
                margin-bottom: 10px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="header-icon">📬</div>
            <h1>Thank You!</h1>
            <p>We've received your message</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hi {{name}},
            </div>

            <div class="thank-you-card">
                <div class="thank-you-message">🎉 Message Received Successfully!</div>
                <div class="thank-you-description">
                    Thank you for reaching out to Quiz-Blog! We appreciate you taking the time to contact us.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="response-timeline">
                <div class="timeline-title">📋 What happens next?</div>
                
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-icon">✅</div>
                    <div class="timeline-text">
                        <strong>Message Received:</strong> Your inquiry has been logged and assigned a reference number
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-icon">👥</div>
                    <div class="timeline-text">
                        <strong>Team Review:</strong> Our support team will review your message within 24 hours
                    </div>
                </div>
                
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="timeline-icon">📧</div>
                    <div class="timeline-text">
                        <strong>Response:</strong> We'll respond to your request, question, or suggestion as soon as possible
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="info-section">
                <div class="info-title">💡 While you wait...</div>
                <div class="info-text">
                    Feel free to explore our platform! Check out our latest quizzes, read our blog articles, 
                    or browse through our study materials to enhance your learning experience.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cta-section">
                <div class="cta-title">🚀 Continue Learning</div>
                <div class="cta-buttons">
                    <a href="https://www.quizblog.rw" class="cta-button">🏠 Homepage</a>
                    <a href="https://www.quizblog.rw/blog" class="cta-button">📖 Blog</a>
                    <a href="https://www.quizblog.rw/about" class="cta-button">ℹ️ About Us</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p style="color: #157A6E; font-weight: 600; font-size: 18px; text-align: center; margin-top: 30px;">
                We value your feedback and look forward to assisting you! 🌟
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <div class="company-info">
                <div class="company-name">Quiz-Blog Rwanda</div>
                <div class="company-tagline">Quizzing & Blogging</div>
                <div class="company-location">📍 Kigali | Rwamagana, Rwanda</div>
            </div>

            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/quiz-blog/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">LinkedIn</a>
                <span class="separator">|</span>
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/QuizblogRw/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">Facebook</a>
                <span class="separator">|</span>
                <a href="https://twitter.com/QuizblogRw" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">Twitter</a>
                <span class="separator">|</span>
                <a href="https://www.instagram.com/quizblogrw/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">Instagram</a>
                <span class="separator">|</span>
                <a href="https://www.quizblog.rw/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">Website</a>
                <span class="separator">|</span>
                <a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send?phone=250780579067" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="social-link">📱 WhatsApp</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>